Z","msg":"食過兩三次無事"},{"pid":"b653a07d985d121ec88f7811fa6f26cca011d9cc","tid":790440,"uid":156018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"魚生呢家野真係好考驗個人腸胃受唔受得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日本人都係咁食成世都冇乜特別問題<br />\n我由細食到大，最愛三文魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個都話三文魚先最出事但so far呢幾廿年都唔覺有咩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明將，爭鮮，元綠呢啲以前差不多日日食，未試過肚痾到要睇醫生/入院，莫講話魚生啦，食野唔睇份量既話係人都搞長沙"},{"pid":"d8e15caa1d031fb5aa47da0a823141a56073661a","tid":790440,"uid":22483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfc05747805552a8ff3d2d8b3d61e77c894bd4db","tid":790440,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"有朋友去完泰國<br />\n返香港之後中甲型肝炎<br />\n入咗醫生幾日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:24:43.000Z","msg":"個醫生最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26b99fb783fa10bfde65d0a751e13ac8526d1b2","tid":790440,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:25:00.000Z","msg":"好撚驚自己生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df12e7ecb6e9b92d8640249cf9152aebf3d383f3","tid":790440,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8e15caa1d031fb5aa47da0a823141a56073661a","tid":790440,"uid":22483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfc05747805552a8ff3d2d8b3d61e77c894bd4db","tid":790440,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"有朋友去完泰國<br />\n返香港之後中甲型肝炎<br />\n入咗醫生幾日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:24:43.000Z","msg":"個醫生最後點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:32:05.000Z","msg":"打錯自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n院"},{"pid":"7ca4c8144cbd575c022d44431137fb765e44bbc3","tid":790440,"uid":38915,"like":0,"dislik